def benchmark(res_consolidado_train, res_consolidado_test, res_consolidado_validacao):
    df = DataFrame(DataFrame(res_consolidado_train).sum()).transpose()  
    df2 = DataFrame(DataFrame(res_consolidado_test).sum()).transpose()  
    df3 = DataFrame(DataFrame(res_consolidado_validacao).sum()).transpose()  
    

    valores = list(df.values[0])
    colunas = list(df.columns)
    
    valores2 = list(df2.values[0])
    colunas2 = list(df2.columns)
    
    valores3 = list(df3.values[0])
    colunas3 = list(df3.columns)

    pyplot.figure(figsize=(20.5, 3))
    
    pyplot.bar(colunas, valores, align='center', color = 'grey', label='Dados de treino')
    
    pyplot.bar(colunas2, valores2, align='center', color = 'gold', bottom=valores, yerr=valores2, label='Dados de teste')
    
    pyplot.bar(colunas3, valores3, align='center', color = 'darkcyan',  bottom=valores2, yerr=valores3, label='Dados de validao')
    
    pyplot.title("Erro Quadrtico Mdio para cada modelo construdo")
    
    pyplot.legend()

def visualizar_resultados(data, pre_processing):
    
    res_consolidado_train = []
    res_consolidado_test = []
    modelos_gerados = {}
    tb_resultado_train = []
    tb_resultado_test = []
    
    
    tb_models = []
    
    for item in Modelo.__subclasses__():
        post = PostProcessor(data, item, pre_processing.scaler, mode = 1)
        post.get_configuration_data()
        post.training_best_nn()
        post.get_results()
        mse_train, mse_test = post.plot_nn_result()
        model = post.get_model()
        tb_resultado_train.append(mse_train)
        tb_resultado_test.append(mse_test)
        
        tb_models.append(model)
        post.save_plot_result(item.__name__)
        
        del post
   
    for i in range(len(tb_models)):
            modelos_gerados.update({[x.__name__ for x in Modelo.__subclasses__()][i]: tb_models[i]})
            
    for i in range(len(tb_resultado_train)):
        res_consolidado_train.append({[x.__name__ for x in Modelo.__subclasses__()][i]: tb_resultado_train[i]})
        
    for i in range(len(tb_resultado_test)):
        res_consolidado_test.append({[x.__name__ for x in Modelo.__subclasses__()][i]: tb_resultado_test[i]})
    
        
    return res_consolidado_train, res_consolidado_test, modelos_gerados

def gerar_previsoes(data, pre_processing, model):
    
    res_consolidado = []

    return res_consolidado

def gerar_dataset(name):
    data = get_csv(name)
    pre_processing = PreProcessor(data)
    pre_processing.normalization()
    pre_processing.sliding_window(x_in=5, y_out=10)
    pre_processing.split_train_test()
    pre_processing.split_in_out(5, 17)
    pre_processing.set_numpy_format()
    data = pre_processing.get_data()
    
    return data, pre_processing

Topologias de redes neurais

class Modelo(Sequential):
    __metaclass__ = abc.ABCMeta
    
    def __init__(self):
        self.tam_saida = 10
        self.batch_size = 32 
        self.verbose = 0
        self.otimizacao = 'rmsprop' 
        self.kernel_init = 'random_uniform'
        self.funcao_ativacao_linear = 'linear'
        
    def custom_tanh(x):
        return 1.7159 * K.tanh((2 / 3) * x)

    def mean_squared_error(y_true, y_pred):
        return K.mean(K.square(y_pred - y_true), axis=-1)
    
        
    @abc.abstractmethod
    def topologia(self):
        "Topologia da rede construda"

class MLPType1(Modelo):
                    
    def topologia(self, train_X, train_y, test_X, test_y, neurons=64, dropout= 0.4, epochs = 50):
        model = Sequential()
        model.add(Dense(train_X.shape[2], input_shape=(1, train_X.shape[2]), activation=Modelo.custom_tanh))
        model.add(Dropout(dropout))
        model.add(Dense(neurons, input_shape=(1, train_X.shape[2]), activation=Modelo.custom_tanh, \
                        kernel_initializer=self.kernel_init))
        model.add(Dense(self.tam_saida, activation=self.funcao_ativacao_linear ))
        model.compile(loss=Modelo.mean_squared_error,
                      optimizer=self.otimizacao ,
                      metrics=[Modelo.mean_squared_error])
        
        history = model.fit(train_X,
                    train_y,
                    batch_size=self.batch_size,
                    epochs = epochs,
                    verbose=self.verbose,
                    validation_data = (test_X,test_y))
    
        return model,history

class MLPType3(Modelo):

class LSTMType1(Modelo):
    def topologia(self, train_X, train_y, test_X, test_y, neurons=64, dropout= 0.4, epochs = 50):
        model = Sequential()
        model.add(Dense(train_X.shape[2], input_shape=(1, train_X.shape[2]), activation=Modelo.custom_tanh))
        model.add(Dropout(dropout))
        model.add(LSTM(train_X.shape[2], input_shape=(1, train_X.shape[2]), activation=Modelo.custom_tanh, return_sequences=True,
                       kernel_initializer=self.kernel_init ))
        model.add(Dense(self.tam_saida, activation=self.funcao_ativacao_linear ))
        model.compile(loss=Modelo.mean_squared_error,
                      optimizer=self.otimizacao ,
                      metrics=[Modelo.mean_squared_error])

        history = model.fit(train_X,
                    train_y,
                    batch_size=self.batch_size,
                    epochs = epochs,
                    verbose=self.verbose,
                    validation_data = (test_X,test_y))
    
        return model,history

Pre Processamento

In [4]:
class PreProcessor:
    
    def __init__(self, data):
        self.data = data
        self.dataset = {}

    def normalization(self):
        columns = self.data.columns
        self.scaler = MinMaxScaler(feature_range = (-1,1))
        self.data = self.scaler.fit_transform(self.data)
        self.data = pd.DataFrame(self.data, columns = columns)
        
    def split_train_test(self, percentual_train = 0.90):
        tam_treino = int(len(self.data) * percentual_train)
        self.dataset['train'], self.dataset['test'] = self.data[0:tam_treino], self.data[tam_treino:len(self.data)]
        
    def sliding_window(self, x_in= 1, y_out= 1, dropnan=True):
        if type(self.data) is list:
            n_vars = 1 
        else: 
            n_vars = self.data.shape[1]
        
        df = DataFrame(self.data)
        cols, names = list(), list()
    
    #Sequencia corrente de entrada
    
        for i in range(x_in, 0, -1):
            aux_1 = df.shift(-i)
            
            cols.append(aux_1)
            for j in aux_1.keys():
                names += [j+' (t)']
        
    # Sequencia de sada 
        
        for i in range(1, y_out+1):
            aux = df.shift(-i)
            cols.append(aux)
            #cols.append(df.shift(-i))
            if i == 1:
                for j in aux.keys():
                    names += [j+' (t+1)']
                
            else:
                for j in aux.keys():
                    names += [j+' (t+%d)' % i]
                
        #Juno dos dados coletados
        
        agg = concat(cols, axis=1)
        agg.columns = names
       
        # Remove registros com itens nulos
        
        if dropnan:
            agg.dropna(inplace=True)
        self.data = agg
        
        
    def split_in_out(self, slide_window_in, col):
        """slide_window_in refere-se a quantidade de pontos da srie utilizado como entrada.
        No caso o modelo atual trabalha com 17 variveis"""
        index = 1
        
        for j in ([self.dataset['train'], self.dataset['test']]):
            
            x = j.iloc[:, :slide_window_in*col] 
            y_list = []
            for i in j.keys():
                if(i[:11] == 'closing (t+'):
                    y_list.append(i)
            y = j[y_list]
            
            if(index == 1):
                self.dataset['train_x'] = DataFrame(x)
                self.dataset['train_y'] = y
            else:
                self.dataset['test_x'] = DataFrame(x)
                self.dataset['test_y'] = y
                
            index += 1
                
         
    def set_numpy_format(self):
        
        def reshape_data(data):
            return reshape(data, (data.shape[0], 1, data.shape[1]))
        
        for k in ('train','test'):
            self.dataset[k+'_x'] = array(self.dataset[k+'_x'])
            self.dataset[k+'_x'] = reshape_data(self.dataset[k+'_x'])
                      
            self.dataset[k+'_y'] = array(self.dataset[k+'_y'])
            self.dataset[k+'_y'] = reshape_data(self.dataset[k+'_y'])
            
    def get_data(self):
        return self.dataset
    
    def get_train_x(self):
        return self.dataset['train_x']
    
    def get_train_y(self):
        return self.dataset['train_y']
    
    def get_test_x(self):
        return self.dataset['test_x']
    
    def get_test_y(self):
        return self.dataset['test_y']
    
    def get_scaler(self):
        return self.scaler

class PostProcessor:
    def __init__(self,data, model, scaler, mode):
        self.raw_model = model
        self.data = data
        self.mode = mode 
        
    def get_configuration_data(self):
        self.source = "grid_search_result"
        self.host = 'ds155268.mlab.com'
        self.collection = 'smartbot_database_tcc'
        self.port = 55268
        self.user_id = 'marcosvgj'
        self.user_password = 'a597179b'
        self.session = MongoClient(self.host, self.port)
        self.configuration = {}
        db2 = self.session[self.collection]
        db2.authenticate(self.user_id, self.user_password)
        cursor = db2[self.collection]
        cursor = cursor.database.get_collection(self.source)
        for items in cursor.find({}):
            self.configuration.update(items)
            
        self.configuration = self.configuration[self.raw_model.__name__]
        
    def training_best_nn(self):
        self.model = self.raw_model()
        self.model_v2, self.history = self.model.topologia(neurons = int(self.configuration['Neurons']), 
                 dropout = int(self.configuration['Dropout']),\
                 train_X = self.data['train_x'],\
                 train_y = self.data['train_y'],\
                 test_X = self.data['test_x'],\
                 test_y = self.data['test_y'],\
                 epochs = self.configuration['Epochs'])

    def get_model(self):
        return self.model_v2
        
    def get_results_by_model(self, model):
        trainPredict = model.predict(self.data['train_x'])
        self.trainPredict_v2 = trainPredict.reshape(trainPredict.shape[0],trainPredict.shape[2])
                                          
        testPredict = model.predict(self.data['test_x'])
        self.testPredict_v2 = testPredict.reshape(testPredict.shape[0],testPredict.shape[2])
    
    def get_results(self):
        
        trainPredict = self.model_v2.predict(self.data['train_x'])
        self.trainPredict_v2 = trainPredict.reshape(trainPredict.shape[0],trainPredict.shape[2])
                                          
        testPredict = self.model_v2.predict(self.data['test_x'])
        self.testPredict_v2 = testPredict.reshape(testPredict.shape[0],testPredict.shape[2])
            
    def plot_nn_result(self):
        
        tb_resultados = []
        
        def consolidar_serie(serie):
            lista_consolidada = []
            lista_consolidada.append(list(serie[0])[0])
            for item in serie[1:]:
                lista_consolidada.append(item[4])
            
            return lista_consolidada   
        
        if(self.mode == 1):
            pyplot.figure(figsize=(20.5, 3))
            pyplot.plot(consolidar_serie(array(self.data['train']['closing (t)'])), 'g-',label='Valor Real')
            pyplot.plot(consolidar_serie(self.trainPredict_v2),'b-', label='Valor Predito')
            pyplot.xlabel("Tempo (dias)")
            pyplot.ylabel("Valores da cotao \n Treino")
            pyplot.legend()
        
            pyplot.title(self.raw_model.__name__)
    
            pyplot.figure(figsize=(20.5, 3))
            pyplot.plot(consolidar_serie(array(self.data['test']['closing (t)'])), 'g-',label='Valor Real')
            pyplot.plot(consolidar_serie(self.testPredict_v2),'b-', label='Valor Predito')
            pyplot.xlabel("Tempo (dias)")
            pyplot.ylabel("Valores da cotao \n Teste ")
            pyplot.legend()
            
            mse_train = mse(array(consolidar_serie(array(self.data['train']['closing (t)']))), \
                                            array(consolidar_serie(self.trainPredict_v2)))
            
            mse_test = mse(array(consolidar_serie(array(self.data['test']['closing (t)']))), \
                                            array(consolidar_serie(self.testPredict_v2)))
            
            return mse_train, mse_test
        
        else:
            pyplot.figure(figsize=(20.5, 3))
            pyplot.plot(consolidar_serie(array(self.data['train']['closing (t)'])), 'g-',label='Valor Real')
            pyplot.plot(consolidar_serie(self.trainPredict_v2),'b-', label='Valor Predito')
            pyplot.title(self.raw_model.__name__)
            pyplot.xlabel("Tempo (dias)")
            pyplot.ylabel("Valores da cotao \n Validao ")
            pyplot.legend()
            
            
            
            return mse(array(consolidar_serie(array(self.data['train']['closing (t)']))), \
                                            array(consolidar_serie(self.trainPredict_v2)))
              
    def save_plot_result(self,name):
        
        def consolidar_serie(serie):
            lista_consolidada = []
            lista_consolidada.append(list(serie[0])[0])
            for item in serie[1:]:
                lista_consolidada.append(item[4])
            
            return lista_consolidada   
        
        """Salva em dois arquivos csv's, os pontos necessrios para plotar o resultado obtido ( previso )"""
        file_name = name
                           
        columns = ['real','predito']

        newpath = r'TCC/resultados/'+file_name
        if not os.path.exists(newpath):
            os.makedirs(newpath)
            # Treino
        treino_ab = DataFrame(data = [consolidar_serie(array(self.data['train']['closing (t)'])),\
                                          consolidar_serie(self.trainPredict_v2)]).transpose()
                    
        treino_ac = DataFrame(treino_ab).rename(columns={0:"Real",1: "Predito"})
        treino_ac.index.name = 'index'
        treino_csv = treino_ac.to_csv(path_or_buf = "TCC/resultados/"+file_name+'/train.csv')

        #Teste
        teste_ab = DataFrame(data = [consolidar_serie(array(self.data['test']['closing (t)'])),\
                                         consolidar_serie(self.testPredict_v2)]).transpose()
        teste_ab = pd.DataFrame(teste_ab).rename(columns={0:"Real",1: "Predito"})
        teste_ab.index.name = 'index'
        teste_csv = teste_ab.to_csv(path_or_buf = "TCC/resultados/"+file_name+'/test.csv')
